# Plugin Boundary

This plugin uses the canonical `src/` authoring layout.

- Edit only files under `src/`.
- Treat plugin-root manifests and config files as generated outputs.
- `plugin-kit-ai generate` may overwrite generated files in the plugin root.

After changing `src/`, run:

```bash
plugin-kit-ai normalize .
plugin-kit-ai generate .
plugin-kit-ai generate --check .
plugin-kit-ai validate . --platform {{.Platform}} --strict
```
